summary: Test suite for the TensorFlow implementation of the GroupViT vision model, validating its configuration, forward pass, attention and hidden state outputs, handling of inputs_embeds, graph execution, saved model generation, pretrained loading, and parity with the PyTorch version.
business_intent: Guarantee that the GroupViT TensorFlow model operates correctly in diverse contexts and aligns with the reference PyTorch implementation, supporting reliable deployment and integration.
